social_posts.post_text: Hands up if you’re ready for summer
Instagram vs reality [SWIPE LEFT]  #imfreezing

I wish this photo could convey to you just how soft this top is.  The fabric is a dream and so is the cut - trust me, you will love it. 

These earrings are another favorite find of mine.  I have somewhat sensitive ears and I haven’t had any issue with these, plus they are super light so you can wear them for long periods of time and be totally fine! 

As always, I’ve linked to everything on my page in the @shop.ltk app!  @saks #SaksPartner #Saks https://liketk.it/3XHGU

One item I’ve wanted to add to my wardrobe is a pair of leather (faux leather) trousers.  For the past two years I’ve tried on many pairs and I am happy to report I finally found one that I love!  You might only think about wearing leather pants to go out at night, so I wanted to show how you can style them for daytime as well. 

As always, I’ve linked to everything on my page in the @shop.ltk app!  @saks #SaksPartner #Saks https://liketk.it/40oWW

Always on the hunt for high waisted jeans and recently found this pair which has quickly become a favorite of mine.  I love the wash and the fabric is also really soft )even though it looks like a more rigid denim). Swipe right to see this outfit paired with my go to winter coat.  It’s the perfect dupe of the designer one I’m sure you all know, but at a fraction of the price. 

I’ve linked to everything on my page in the @shop.ltk app!  @saks #SaksPartner #Saks https://liketk.it/42VFT

Even though I’ve always loved wearing belts with dresses, it was only recently that I discovered how much I also love pairing them with jeans and pants.  The finish (faux croc) and color (dark brown) of this belt makes it super versatile and easy to dress up or down! 

As always I’ve linked to everything on my page in the @shop.ltk app!  @saks #SaksPartner #Saks https://liketk.it/45xAQ

Spring is here, which means it’s time to break out the jean jacket! I love throwing a jean jacket over a summer dress to make it more weather appropriate and also give it a more casual and chill vibe!
